job.title: IGCAR Stipendiary Trainee Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for 337 Vacancies in Tamilnadu
job.body:
Total Vacancies:337

Name of the post:

  • Stipendiary Trainee, Technical Officer & Others

Description:

Indira Gandhi Centre for Atomic Research issued a total of 337 vacancies for the posts of Stipendiary Trainee, Technical Officer & Others. The online application for these vacancies in Tamilnadu under IGCAR shall start from 15.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 14.05.2021 . For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for IGCAR Stipendiary Trainee Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 15.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 03.06.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have a diploma or degree in 10th, 12th, ITI, Diploma, Degree, B.E, B.Tech, Ph.D. to apply for the post of Stipendiary Trainee, Technical Officer & Others

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 21 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 35 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the vacancies of Stipendiary Trainee, Technical Officer & Others is: Rs 16,000 - 78,800 per month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that IGCAR  issued this notification for which vacancies.

How to apply for IGCAR Stipendiary Trainee Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of IGCAR 
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Stipendiary Trainee, Technical Officer & Others.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
